thread.title: Zoe Velez (Flamenkisimo Sydney)
thread.title_full: Ticketebo reviewed by Zoe Velez (Flamenkisimo Sydney)

author: Zoe Velez (Flamenkisimo Sydney)
title: Zoe Velez (Flamenkisimo Sydney)
text:
I've used other ticketing websites in the past and Ticketebo is by far the best. The individual webpage created for your event looks fantastic and the information is displayed really well. I think it boosts sales as it looks so good.
The app to scan the tickets, is easy to use and so effecient. Being able to scan tickets at the door is brilliant.
The daily sales report and other reports generated by the app are so useful. Plus, the service received from staff was excellent.
Highly recommend!
